OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FMostly dry
OL,6,Fto start with sunny spells and just
OL,7,Fthe odd shower. Turning somewhat
OL,8,Fcloudier overnight with a few showers
OL,9,Fbut still some dry, clear spells.
OL,10,FStrong winds will ease.
OL,11,
OL,12,CFriday:FBright or sunny spells and
OL,13,Fvariable cloud throughout the day.
OL,14,FMostly dry but the odd light shower
OL,15,Fpossible. Winds freshen in the
OL,16,Fafternoon.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
